2026-03-30T10:51:58.8601132Z               "message": "Fix hanging test: replace ExecuteAsync tight loop with direct PollAllHubsAsync calls\n\nThe ExecuteAsync_ErrorInPollCycle_ContinuesRunning test used IntervalMinutes=0\nwhich caused Task.Delay(TimeSpan.Zero) to complete synchronously, creating an\ninfinite synchronous loop that blocked StartAsync from returning. Replaced with\ndirect PollAllHubsAsync calls that verify error recovery without ExecuteAsync.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01RCLYJgpNTTjg2qDExbZ2vv",
