2026-03-30T10:51:58.8610980Z               "message": "Fix DST crash in activity summaries (#0190) and zigbee status enum (#0192)\n\n#0190: Replace direct TimeZoneInfo.ConvertTimeToUtc calls with\nSendTimeHelper.SafeConvertToUtc in EmailRenderer and Admin Detail page\nto prevent ArgumentException during DST spring-forward gaps. Made\nSafeConvertToUtc public for cross-project reuse.\n\n#0192: Fix HueZigbeeConnectivityResource.Status XML doc comment to list\npending_discovery instead of configuration_error (per Hue CLIP v2 spec).\nAdd pending_discovery case to EmailRenderer status switch. Keep\nconfiguration_error handling as defensive fallback.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01RCLYJgpNTTjg2qDExbZ2vv",
